quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  72,14,"Ne toto mwifwe balimwo Abasalamu nende abalekha katoto. Ne balia basilima, abo nibo baloonda obulunjifu."
  72,15,"Ne balia balekha obwatoto, baliba tsikhwi tsia omulilo kwa Jahannam."
  72,16,"Ne balunjikhanga khunjila yatoto, khwakhabanywesie amaatsi amaanji."
  72,17,"Kho khubateme khuko. Ne ulia uhelesia ametsulisio ka Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi omukongo, alanyoola eshinyasio eshilulu.'”"
  72,18,"Ne toto emisikiti ni chia Nyasaye, kho mulalaama halala nende Nyasaye shiosishiosi tawe."
  72,19,"Ne toto olwa Omusumba wa Nyasaye yasinjila namulaama, (amajini) ako kali hambi muno okhumufwinya!"
  72,20,"Boola mbu: “Toto esie enamanga sa Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, ne shemutsokaasinjiakhwo nende yesiyesi tawe.”"
  72,21,"Boola mbu: “Esie embula obunyali bwokhubawumisia nohomba okhubalunjisia tawe.”"
  72,22,"Boola mbu: “Toto abulaho yesiyesi unyala okhuuninda okhurulana nende eshinyasio shia Nyasaye tawe, ne shindilinyoola wandakhelushila tawe halali khuye.""
  72,23,"Halali okhusia (amakhuwa) okhurula khu Nyasaye nende oburume bubwe. Ne uloba okhutiila ka Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, toto alinyoola Omulilo kwa Jahannam, alimenyamwo tsinyanga tsioosi."
  72,24,"Okhula olwa balilola kabalakungwa, balimanya mbu ni wina omuteshele muno mubukhoonyi nende omuleemu muno khushichelo."
  72,25,"Boola mbu: “Esie engorwa kamulakungwa kano mbu kali ahambi nohomba Nyasaye wanje Omulesi alakasitia ehale.”"
  72,26,"Omumanyi wakefisile, ne shafunulilanga yesiyesi akefisa keke tawe."
  72,27,"Halali ulia wayachamila Mubarumwa. Ne toto oyo amwelesinjia abalindi imbeli wuwe nende inyuma wuwe."
  72,28,"Kho anyoole okhumanya mbu toto bosia oburume bwa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, naye yaterera obulayi akabali ninako, ne yamanya obubasio bwa buli eshindu."